    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning, showroom-quality vehicle! It is in truly mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. From the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, every detail has been meticulously cared for. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants the very best!",
