      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks and feels great. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty won't let you down. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to make someone else just as happy as it made me. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3, powered by the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving unit features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains thermally stable thanks to an efficient oil-to-air cooling circuit. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the rotating assembly. This example represents a solid driver-quality specimen with a taut suspension and a healthy powertrain.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly serviced. Mechanicals are sound. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a blend of performance and comfort that is hard to find. The exterior finish maintains a brilliant gloss, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use like small stone chips on the front fascia. Step inside to a cabin that feels remarkably fresh; the leather upholstery is supple with only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or fading. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced religiously, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection already completed. The engine runs quiet and strong, while the suspension provides a smooth, composed ride over varied terrain. Garage-kept and owned by a non-smoker, this car is ready for its next chapter with a driver who appreciates a well-cared-for machine.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance, it features a well-appointed interior and a robust powertrain. This selection represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a sophisticated balance of reliability and value. We invite you to experience the caliber of this offering firsthand.",
      "price": 34900.0,
